OL,3,CLawyer jailed for seven months for
OL,4,Cmultiple driving offences
OL,6,FA Jersey defence lawyer has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to seven months in prison
OL,8,Fand disqualified from driving for 30
OL,9,Fmonths after drunkenly crashing his
OL,10,Fcar into another and driving off.
OL,12,FDavid Steenson, 57, admitted failing
OL,13,Fto stop after an accident, drink-
OL,14,Fdriving and two counts of dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving.
