OL,3,CLawyer jailed for seven months for
OL,4,Cmultiple driving offences
OL,6,FJersey Magistrate's Court heard how,
OL,7,Fon 16 May 2025, police were called to
OL,8,FSt John, where a white Mini Cooper had
OL,9,Fbeen struck by Steenson's vehicle,
OL,10,Fwhich had then driven away - and was
OL,11,Flater found more than a mile up the
OL,12,Froad.
OL,14,FPolice had been able to follow marks
OL,15,Fleft by a damaged wheel on Steenson's
OL,16,FJaguar which had grinded with the
OL,17,Ftarmac.
OL,19,FSteenson claims he thought he had hit
OL,20,Fa curb or a wall.
