OL,3,CLawyer jailed for seven months for
OL,4,Cmultiple driving offences
OL,6,FAn alcohol breath test showed he had
OL,7,F82 micrograms of alcohol in 100
OL,8,Fmillilitres of breath - which is more
OL,9,Fthan double the legal limit (35mg).
OL,11,FIt's the second time that the criminal
OL,12,Fadvocate has appeared at the
OL,13,FMagistrate's Court in the last 12
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FIn December, he was sentenced to 130
OL,17,Fhours of community service and forced
OL,18,Fto pay #2,419.55 of compensation after
OL,19,Fpleading guilty to attacking a taxi
OL,20,Fdriver whilst drunk.
