OL,3,CLawyer jailed for seven months for
OL,4,Cmultiple driving offences
OL,6,FHe was also suspended from practicing
OL,7,Flaw in the island for three months.
OL,9,FThere were two people in the Mini
OL,10,FCooper at the time of the crash, and
OL,11,Fthe driver suffered whiplash,
OL,12,Fexperienced sleeping issues and had to
OL,13,Ftake time off of work.
OL,15,FThe defence confirmed that Steenson
OL,16,Fhad consumed wine while meeting
OL,17,Fsomeone to discuss a legal matter
OL,18,Fbefore the collision.
